How to Catch a Lie
A quick look at the latest headlines shows just how serious and pervasive deception and lies are in everyday life.
Republican presidential candidate Herman Kane is busy challenging allegations of sexual harassment from multiple women; each side accuses the other of lying.
The University of Pennsylvania administration was charged with perjury because they allegedly concealed that a retired football coach had raped boys.
